"{\"uid\": \"keyt.com-news-2024-01-01-2-men-arrested-in-connection-with-ugandan-olympic-runners-killing-in-kenya-police-say\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By TOM ODULAAssociated Press  NAIROBI, Kenya (AP) - Police say two men have been arrested in connection with the killing of Ugandan Oympic runner Benjamin Kiplagat, who was found fatally stabbed in a car in Kenya on New Year's Eve.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Protecting_group\", \"score\": 0.9999999665224101, \"rank\": 2.846558892214443e-08, \"text\": \"TOM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Protecting_group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Protecting_group\"}, {\"begin\": 30, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\", \"score\": 0.9999973617268111, \"rank\": 2.631980189180098e-06, \"text\": \"NAIROBI\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\"}, {\"begin\": 39, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999666275704, \"rank\": 3.161904558984948e-08, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999776492742397, \"rank\": 2.1859828637720664e-05, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Kiplagat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Benjamin Kiplagat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Kiplagat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Kiplagat\"}, {\"begin\": 207, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999666275704, \"rank\": 3.161904558984948e-08, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A police official says a knife suspected to have been used in the killing of the 34-year-old Kiplagat was found on one of the suspects.\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The official says the motive for the killing appears to have been robbery because money and a cell phone had been taken from Kiplagat.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiplagat was found dead in his brother's car on Sunday on the outskirts of Eldoret, a high-altitude town in western Kenya renowned as a training base for elite athletes.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999666275704, \"rank\": 3.161904558984948e-08, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jump to comments \\u2193  News Channel 3-12 is committed to providing a forum for civil and constructive conversation.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please keep your comments respectful and relevant.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can review our Community Guidelines byclicking here  If you would like to share a story idea, please submit ithere.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Terms of Service  Privacy Policy  Community Guidelines  FCC Public File  EEO Public File Report  FCC Applications  Do Not Sell My Personal Information  Daily News UpdateWeather ForecastBreaking NewsSevere WeatherContests & P